 This listing is for one of 8 layered Trilogy Necklaces

Long, layered necklaces featuring beautiful natural stone pendants dipped in 24k Gold and delicate Rosary style chains made with natural gemstones.

DESCRIPTION BY NUMBER
1. ANTLER/DRUZY NECKLACE: Antler charm in Sterling Silver. White Agate Druzy pendant in Sterling Silver.

3. RAW AMETHYST/DRUZY: Amethyst Geode pendant with 22k Vermeil Bezel. Titanium Agate Druzy 24k Gold Dipped. Labradorite Rosary style chain. 
4. CRESCENT MOON/LAPIS TEARDROP: Lapis pendant with 22k Vermeil Bezel. Iolite Rosary style chain. Combination pictured available in Gold only.
5. ARROWHEAD/TRIANGLE DRUZY: Quartz Arrowhead 24k Gold Dipped. Druzy 24k Gold Dipped. Rainbow Moonstone Rosary style chain. Combination pictured available in Gold only.
6. ANTLER/QUATREFOIL DRUZY: Magnesite pendant 24kGold Dipped. Rosary style chain. Combination pictured available in Gold only.
7. TRIANGLE/SQUARE DRUZY: Both Druzy pendants are 24k Gold Dipped. Iolite Rosary style chain. Combination pictured available in Gold only.
8. QUARTZ/LOTUS: Rock Quartz point pendant. Rainbow Moonstone Rosary style chain. 

MEASUREMENTS
The shortest layer from 30” to 34” -plus about an inch of charm/pendant.
You can also specify your preferred length in the notes to seller at checkout. 

VARIATIONS 
Let me know if you are interested in specific colors or charms. I’m sure that I can accommodate your request. :-) 

CUSTOM 
I am always happy to make multiples or custom orders. For example: if you like a particular design, it can be made using different gemstones and colors. If a particular stone or pendant appeals to you, it could be fashioned into the design of your choice.

WEDDINGS
I love making Wedding Jewelry and multiples as Bridesmaid Gifts.

If you are interested in Weddings, multiples, or custom orders, let me know your preferences in the notes to seller at checkout.

PRECIOUS METALS
All chains and clasps are 14k Gold Filled or Sterling Silver.
All charms are 22k Vermeil or Sterling Silver. 
Bezels, Wire Wrapped Genuine Gemstones are 22k Gold Vermeil or Sterling Silver. 



SO MANY PRECIOUS METALS - WHAT'S THE DIFFERENCE?

VERMEIL is Sterling Silver with a 1-2 micron plating of 18k - 24k gold on top.

GOLD FILLED is an actual layer of gold, pressure bonded to another metal. Gold filled is not to be confused with gold plating, as filled literally has 100% more gold than gold plating. Gold filled is much more valuable and tarnish resistant. Gold filled jewelry is an economical alternative to solid gold!

STERLING SILVER is 92.5% pure silver with some base metal for strength.

FINE SILVER from the Thai Karen Hill Tribe is 97-99% pure silver, a little softer than sterling but very tarnish resistant.

results.title: Mid Century Retro Chrome & Metal Desk - Vintage 1960s Student Desk - Retro Modern Petite Desk
results.description:
A Mid Century Chrome & Metal writing desk, circa 1960s.

Ready for a new life in your home or office space, this retro modern desk has a sturdy steel frame, laminate desktop, under desk shelf and chrome legs. The bright red metal accents make this pop in any room, and the chrome looks as if it was garage kept for all these years. This authentic vintage piece was probably used for upper elementary through Jr. high school students, featuring a durable laminate desk top, with a really cool adjustable top surface to accommodate different height levels!

Finished on all sides this totally retro desk can be placed anywhere in a room. The chrome frame lends well to retro or modern design aesthetics, and the red metal frame adds a pop of color. Notice the top surface height can be adjusted with a simple turn of the crank below. There is also a small storage compartment to the bottom right.

The chrome frame is in excellent condition, with no rust or patina at all. The durable laminate top has light age appropriate wear, and the drop-down hand crank feature moves up and down with ease. The red metal accents are all original and show some light age appropriate wear.

CONDITION:
Very good vintage condition. Light age appropriate wear. 
Chrome frame has some light scratches and all four of the flour gliders/protectors are in place. 
Laminate top is also in very good shape with a few light scratches and scuffs. 
The metal body is structurally sound, durable and very HEAVY!
+++++

results.title: New Baby Girl Gift - Personalised Heart Produced in Your Choice of Fabric. Supplied Gift Boxed
results.description:
A perfect little present for a new born baby girl. 

These lovely little fabric hearts make a gorgeous keepsake gifts to give to parents of new baby girls. The hearts can be personalised with the new baby's name, date of birth and weight. The design is then completed with the sweet little quote 'Sometimes the smallest things take up the most room in your heart' (We are happy to change this to something else should you prefer)

To create your personalised heart, first choose the fabric you would like it to be made in. We have 20 options available so there's something to suit everyone (please see the product images for current options available)

Then, let us know the wording you would like printing by adding a note in the 'note to seller' section during checkout - the image shown is just an example, we can write anything you like (subject to it fitting in the available space). If you are unsure whether your message will fit just send us a message and we would be happy to advise.

We will then carefully create your WordHeart, filling it with a combination of scented dried lavender & a quality polyester stuffing, before carefully packaging it into one of our WordHeart gift boxes.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* * *ORDERS OUTSIDE OF EUROPE - PLEASE NOTE* * *
Due to import restrictions, orders being sent to countries outside of Europe (i.e. America, Canada, New Zealand & Australia) will be filled with a combination of lavender scented Aroma Beads & a quality polyester stuffing rather than dried lavender.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

We appreciate that some people aren't as madly in love with the scent of lavender as we are, so if you would prefer your heart to made without the lavender simply select the 'No Lavender Scent' option when ordering.

The heart will be made from your chosen fabric on the front and will have a plain cream cotton back. The personalised wording will be printed on to a cotton panel and then stitched to the front of the heart. A button decoration and rustic twine hanging loop are then added to finish the heart off perfectly.

**SIZE**
The heart measures approximately 11cm x 11cm (4 inch x 4 inch).

** POSTAGE & DELIVERY TIMES **
Your personalised Word Heart will be lovingly stitched and then carefully packed and despatched within 4 working days of ordering.  Order sent within the UK are posted by 1st class delivery which typically takes 1-2 days.  Orders being sent overseas are sent via Airmail post.  This typically takes 3 - 5 WORKING days to reach European destinations and 5 - 7 WORKING days to reach the US, Canada, Australia and New Zealand however occasionally delivery times may be longer due to your countries customs / postal service.

**CUSTOM ORDERS**
I have lots of other Word Hearts with various phrases in my Etsy shop so please have a browse, if there is nothing suitable I can also make custom Word Hearts in a variety of fabrics and a phrase of your choosing, please ask for details.

**SAFETY**
This heart is intended as a decoration only. It is not a toy and should be kept out of the reach of children.

results.title: 300 Plantable confetti hearts- choose from 16 colors - homemade paper mixed with wildflower seeds- ecofriendly- earth day
results.description:
Plantable Paper Hearts
SET OF 300

Our seed paper is hand made using recycled paper- very ecofriendly!  It is made with a blend of wildflower seeds that get mixed into the paper making process as we press full sheets of paper.  After the paper is finished drying, we then hand-punch out each little shape with love!  It is a tedious process, but it is very rewarding to create a 'green' product to be enjoyed by others.

Plantables and Paper prides itself with giving you the most 'bang for your buck.'  We give you the most seeds per shape than any other shop on Etsy!  You can see a multitude of seeds in every little confetti piece!

Our hearts measure approximately 1 inch wide.  Please view photos with a quarter for size comparison.

White, Ivory-Cream, Red, Pink, Orange, Peachy-Salmon, Bright Yellow, Light Yellow, Grass Green, Light Green, Robin Egg Blue, Light Blue, Purple, Light Purple, Gray, Chocolate Brown

Seeds used are a blend of annuals and perennials including but not limited to:
Catchfly, Snapdragon, Red Prairie Coneflower, Daisy, Sweet Alyssum, White Yarrow, Poppy, Sweet William
